<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Flyobo Travel Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4B0082;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 25px 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4B0082;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px dashed #4B0082;
        }
        .warning {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: #FFD700;">Flyobo Travel</span>!</h1>
            <p>Let's get your account verified.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">To complete your registration and secure your account, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <span class="otp-code"><%= otp %></span>
            </div>

            <p class="warning">⚠️ This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Need help? Feel free to reply to this email or contact our support team.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 40px;">With gratitude,<br/><strong>The Flyobo Travel Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Flyobo Travel. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 